      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，把Path、TopK、UserQuery包在FinTech_PaymentGateway子图里。这三个节点的类型能确认一下吗？我看Path和TopK都是TransactionQueue，UserQuery是LedgerService？",
